Twitter is thirsty for a nice, tall glass of James McAvoy. “Hold on,” you may be thinking. “James McAvoy? The Scottish actor who played Professor X in the X-Men movies?” Yes. “The dude from ‘Atonement,’ right?”  Yup. “Well,” you may reply. “He’s always been handsome, what’s the big deal?” Well, let us introduce you to James McAvoy 2.0: Photographers spotted and snapped photos of freshly swole McAvoy roaming the streets of Philadelphia on Friday. Twitter approved of the 38-year-old actor’s new look. Good job, James.